overview: Free-scoring Arsenal thrilled fans with their unique, high-tempo, slick passing style. This release features every Arsenal goal in all competitions during the 2005/06 season. Highlights of the season include Henry beating Ian Wright's club scoring record, the 7-0 hammering of Middlesborough, and we say goodbye to two Arsenal legends - Bergkamp and Highbury.
title: Arsenal: Season Review 2005-2006
